    "586936e4-8228-4165-9e63-a482af8f5e37": {
      "type": "services-content",
      "blocks": {
        "5217c7aa-3507-4797-b03d-bd44f5fa4bd0": {
          "type": "Image",
          "settings": {
            "image1": "shopify://shop_images/busi2_nessman-handshake-with-engineering-in-construc-2023-03-23-02-15-11-utc_1_80.jpg",
            "video_alignment": "right",
            "title": "Turn Your Store into a Sales Powerhouse: Renovations by Vanguard Store Fixtures",
            "video_description": "<p>At Vanguard Store Fixtures, we recognize that successful retail isn't just about what you sell, but where you sell it. Your store environment is a vital part of your brand, and our store renovation services are designed to ensure your retail space is not just a place to shop, but an experience to remember. With us, your renovation isn't just a makeover, but a strategic reinvention of your space.</p>"
          }
        },
        "f08b2c08-e4e4-4dca-b01a-26204fe57759": {
          "type": "Image",
          "settings": {
            "image1": "shopify://shop_images/2_renovation-2021-09-24-03-37-04-utc_75.jpg",
            "video_alignment": "left",
            "title": "",
            "video_description": "<p>We bring an unparalleled understanding of the retail industry to our renovation projects. Our approach combines practical considerations with innovative design principles, ensuring that every aspect of your renovated store, from the layout to the fixtures, maximizes customer engagement and boosts sales. We see the potential in every space and work to realize it in ways that align with your brand and business goals. Some of the retail stores we renovate include:</p><ul><li>GROCERY STORE</li><li>HARDWARE STORE</li><li>COSMETIC STORE</li><li>CONVENIENCE STORE</li><li>CLOTHING STORE</li><li>JEWELRY STORE</li><li>OPTICAL STORE</li><li>GAS STATION</li><li>PET STORE</li><li>PHARMACY</li><li>BAKERY</li><li>AND MANY OTHER!</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "7f41db2f-43eb-48ad-97f9-669009598141": {
          "type": "Image",
          "settings": {
            "image1": "shopify://shop_images/2_workers-do-concrete-screed-on-floor-with-heating-i-2022-12-16-11-04-27-utc_75.jpg",
            "video_alignment": "right",
            "title": "",
            "video_description": "<p>We specialize in the science of shopping and understand the psychology of the customer. By strategically using elements like lighting, color, and space, we create a shopping environment that appeals to your customers' emotions and instincts, encouraging them to stay longer, explore further, and purchase more. With us, your renovation becomes a tool for influencing customer behavior and driving revenue:</p><ul><li><strong>Brand Alignment:</strong> Ensures space enhances and conveys brand identity.</li><li><strong>Space Utilization:</strong> Maximizes product display and ensures customer comfort.</li><li><strong>Lighting:</strong> Highlights products, creates ambiance, and guides shoppers.</li><li><strong>Flow:</strong> Directs customer traffic to influence purchase path.</li><li><strong>Fixtures:</strong> Enhances product display and accessibility.</li><li><strong>Flexibility:</strong> Allows for easy changes to suit seasonal or promotional needs.</li><li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> Incorporates eco-friendly designs and materials.</li><li><strong>Technology Integration:</strong> Enhances customer interaction and modernizes shopping experience.</li><li><strong>Signage and Graphics:</strong> Helps navigation and communicates promotions effectively.</li><li><strong>Customer Experience:</strong> Promotes a positive shopping experience to increase sales.</li><li><strong>AODA Compliance:</strong> Ensures store accessibility for all customers, meeting Accessibility for Ontarians with Disabilities Act standards.</li><li><strong>Security Considerations:</strong> Balances visibility and safety, accounting for theft prevention and Canadian building code compliant emergency exits.</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "81461937-27d1-40d8-9cf1-04bc408abd07": {
          "type": "Image",
          "settings": {
            "image1": "shopify://shop_images/2_pexels-antonio-sokic-3839432_75.jpg",
            "video_alignment": "left",
            "title": "",
            "video_description": "<p>Trust your renovation project to Vanguard Store Fixtures, where we blend industry expertise with a deep understanding of consumer psychology. As pioneers in the store fixtures industry, we use high-quality, durable materials designed to showcase your merchandise effectively and boost sales. Leveraging the latest trends in retail design, we utilize our skills to offer you the best in store planning and fixture installation. With a strong focus on optimizing store layouts and product displays, our solutions are search-engine-optimized to attract businesses looking for top-notch store renovations. Allow us to transform your retail space into an exciting, immersive shopping environment that drives your business forward. Partner with us today and let's create a retail space that truly embodies your brand, increases your online visibility, and captures the imagination of your customers.</p>"
          }
        }
